title: INTENSE U.S. LINE BATTLE - Regiments of American Revolution Mod Gameplay
description:
Regiments of American Revolution Mod Gameplay - This is my first look at a new mod for Empire total war.  It is a mod that is based of the American Revolution!  In this battle I command American and taking on Jackiefish who is commanding Great Britain. Enjoy the Battle :D 

Mod Link: http://www.moddb.com/mods/regiments-of-american-revolution

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/HighOnTea

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
